{"id":194,"parent_id":193,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":194,"title":"Joshua 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Josh.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1","content":[["div",[".title","The Book of",["br"],["span.dominant","Joshua"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord speaks to Joshua—He is commanded to be of good courage, to meditate upon the law, and to keep the commandments—He prepares Israel to enter Canaan."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.1","order":"02.07.001.17607"},["b","1"],"Now after the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"death"],"of Moses the servant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"it came to pass, that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake unto Joshua the son of Nun, Moses’ minister, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.2","order":"02.07.001.17608"},["b","2"],"Moses my servant is dead; now therefore arise, go over this Jordan, thou, and all this people, unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"land"],"which I do give to them,",["i","even"],"to the children of Israel."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.3","order":"02.07.001.17609"},["b","3"],"Every place that the sole of your foot shall tread upon, that have I given unto you, as I said unto Moses."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.4","order":"02.07.001.17610"},["b","4"],"From the wilderness and this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Lebanon"],"even unto the great river, the river Euphrates, all the land of the Hittites, and unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"great sea"],"toward the going down of the sun, shall be your",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"coast"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.5","order":"02.07.001.17611"},["b","5"],"There shall not any man be able to stand before thee all the days of thy life: as I was with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Moses"],",",["i","so"],"I will be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"with thee"],": I will not fail thee, nor",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"forsake"],"thee."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.6","order":"02.07.001.17612"},["b","6"],"Be strong and of a good",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"courage"],": for unto this people shalt thou",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"divide"],"for an",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"inheritance"],"the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"land"],", which I sware unto their fathers to give them."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.7","order":"02.07.001.17613"},["b","7"],"Only be thou strong and very",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"courageous"],", that thou mayest observe to do according to all the law, which Moses my servant commanded thee:",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"turn"],"not from it",["i","to"],"the right hand or",["i","to"],"the left, that thou mayest",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_7c"},"prosper"],"whithersoever thou goest."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.8","order":"02.07.001.17614"},["b","8"],"This book of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"law"],"shall not depart out of thy mouth; but thou shalt",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"meditate"],"therein day and night, that thou mayest observe to do according to all that is written therein: for then thou shalt make thy way prosperous, and then thou shalt have good success."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.9","order":"02.07.001.17615"},["b","9"],"Have not I commanded thee? Be strong and of a good courage; be not afraid, neither be thou dismayed: for the",["span.smallCaps",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Lord"]],"thy God",["i","is"],"with thee whithersoever thou goest."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.10","order":"02.07.001.17616"},["b","10"],"¶Then Joshua commanded",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"the"],"officers of the people, saying,"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.11","order":"02.07.001.17617"},["b","11"],"Pass through",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"the host"],", and command the people, saying, Prepare you",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"victuals"],"; for within three days ye shall pass over this Jordan, to go in to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"possess"],"the land, which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God giveth you to possess it."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.12","order":"02.07.001.17618"},["b","12"],"¶And to the Reubenites, and to the Gadites, and to half the tribe of Manasseh, spake Joshua, saying,"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.13","order":"02.07.001.17619"},["b","13"],"Remember the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"word"],"which Moses the servant of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"commanded you, saying, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God hath given you",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"rest"],", and hath given you this land."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.14","order":"02.07.001.17620"},["b","14"],"Your wives, your little ones, and your cattle, shall remain in the land which Moses gave you on this side Jordan; but ye shall pass before your brethren armed, all the mighty men of valour, and help them;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.15","order":"02.07.001.17621"},["b","15"],"Until the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have given your brethren rest, as",["i","he hath given"],"you, and they also have possessed the land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God giveth them: then ye shall return unto the land of your possession, and enjoy it, which Moses the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s servant gave you on this side Jordan toward the sunrising."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.16","order":"02.07.001.17622"},["b","16"],"¶And they answered Joshua, saying, All that thou commandest us we will do, and whithersoever thou sendest us, we will go."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.17","order":"02.07.001.17623"},["b","17"],"According as we hearkened unto Moses in all things, so will we hearken unto thee: only the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God be with thee, as he was with Moses."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.18","order":"02.07.001.17624"},["b","18"],"Whosoever",["i","he be"],"that doth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"rebel"],"against thy commandment, and will not hearken unto thy words in all that thou commandest him, he shall be put to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"death"],": only be strong and of a good courage."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.1a","order":"02.07.001.17625"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.50.48-50"},"Deut. 32:50 (48–50)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/34.5.1-8"},"34:5 (1–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.2a","order":"02.07.001.17627"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/13.15.14-17"},"Gen. 13:15 (14–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/15.18.18-21"},"15:18 (18–21)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.4a","order":"02.07.001.17629"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/3.25"},"Deut. 3:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.4b","order":"02.07.001.17631"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/23.31.31-33"},"Ex. 23:31 (31–33)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/34.6.2-12"},"Num. 34:6 (2–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.4c","order":"02.07.001.17633"},["b","4c"],["span.small","IE"],"boundary, border."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.5a","order":"02.07.001.17635"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.91.91-92"},"D&C 107:91 (91–92)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/josh/1.5b","order":"02.07.001.17637"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/31.8.6-8,23"},"Deut. 31:8 (6–8, 23)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/6.27"},"Josh. 6:27"],";",["a.scriptu